# Wiring

The OLED display uses I²C communication.

## OLED Display

| OLED | ESP32-S2 Mini |
| ---- | ------------- |
| VCC  | 3.3V          |
| GND  | GND           |
| SDA  | GPIO 9        |
| SCL  | GPIO 12       |

## Push Button

| Button     | ESP32-S2 Mini |
| ---------- | ------------- |
| One pin    | GPIO 0        |
| Second pin | GND           |

The internal pull-up resistor of the ESP32 is used, so no external resistor is required.

